            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# Parrocchettami 1.0.11

### Security
- Subprocess environments restricted to minimal variables (no shell secrets)
- System opusdec fallback disabled during transcription (bundle only)
- Transcription history file permissions set to owner-only (chmod 600)
- Explicit NSAppTransportSecurity in Info.plist

### Fixes
- Keyboard shortcuts (space/return) now work during recording
- Cancel button guards against overlapping transcriptions
- Delete confirmation dialog for individual history entries
- Resumable model downloads (cancelled downloads pick up where they left off)
- Raw recording preserved if CAF-to-WAV conversion fails
]]></description>
